Package com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.device

package com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.device
This package provides classes to establish and maintain a connection to a TSL Reader
  • Related Packages

    com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol
    This package provides the AsciiCommander class used to execute the ASCII command classes and the DeviceProperties class that describes specific details about the currently connected reader

    This package provides classes representing commands that can be sent to a TSL ASCII 2 protocol Reader

    This package provides custom enumeration classes for ASCII protocol commands
    com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.parameters
    This package provides interfaces and helper classes for the parameters that are used in ASCII protocol commands
    com.uk.tsl.rfid.asciiprotocol.responders
    This package provides classes and interfaces used to manage the ResponderChain for incoming responses from a TSL Reader
